title: Borders, 1900–1924
provenance: Removed from an album in which were mounted 195 samples verso: Ericson & Weiss, Designers, 13 E. 30th Street, New York; 1265M; ..r Yd.
description: These samples have all been removed from a scrapbook that contained 195 examples of wallpaper borders. Sample -102 contains moon and stars that could be for children.
